last_episode_to_air.name: The Last Light
last_episode_to_air.overview: The remaining members of the group fight back enemies, both living and dead, on their quest to save the future.

name: The Walking Dead: World Beyond
overview: A heroic group of teens sheltered from the dangers of the post-apocalyptic world receive a message that inspires them to leave the safety of the only home they have ever known and embark on a cross-country journey to find the one man who can possibly save the world.
tagline: The end of the world was our beginning.

episodes.name: Brave
episodes.overview: Iris welcomes an enigmatic ally to their community while Hope questions the visitor's motives. A message upends the sisters' worldview, forcing them to decide between the safety of their home and the uncertainty of the world beyond.

episodes.name: The Blaze of Gory
episodes.overview: The group adjusts to the reality of life beyond the walls of their community. Iris tries to take over, despite Hope's reservations. Felix and Huck follow the teenagers, while Felix is ​​forced to face unwanted memories.

episodes.name: The Tyger and the Lamb
episodes.overview: Overwhelmed by the past, group members adopt opposite strategies to deal with a huge obstacle. Pressure on the group to return home.

episodes.name: The Wrong End of a Telescope
episodes.overview: The group seeks shelter from a storm inside an abandoned school. While supplying, they imagine what life was like in high school and encounter new threats, both alive and dead.

episodes.name: Madman Across the Water
episodes.overview: While the group works together to cross the Mississippi River, a plot to take the teenagers home hits an obstacle. A group member must overcome past traumas to save others from an oncoming threat.

episodes.name: Shadow Puppets
episodes.overview: When an unexpected newcomer reveals information that can help them reach their destination, the group makes a deal. While some are intrigued by the new arrival, others are suspicious.

episodes.name: Truth or Dare
episodes.overview: While the group is looking for something to advance their search, one of them remembers their struggles in the early days of the apocalypse. A game of truth or challenge brings emotions to the surface.

episodes.name: The Sky Is a Graveyard
episodes.overview: A horrible discovery finds the group at a crossroads and leads one of them to revisit past traumas.

episodes.name: The Deepest Cut
episodes.overview: A series of setbacks causes a member of the group to reevaluate their role in the mission. Someone makes an amazing discovery. A surprising revelation casts everything in a new light.

episodes.name: In This Life
episodes.overview: A divided group struggles to get together. Others turn to the greater good.

episodes.name: Konsekans
episodes.overview: Hope's commitment to the future is put to the test, jeopardizing a potential reunion. Iris and Felix meet a new group. Startling revelations are made.

episodes.name: Foothold
episodes.overview: While some members of the group enact a plan to cover their tracks, others attempt to acclimate to their new surroundings.

episodes.name: Exit Wounds
episodes.overview: An attempted grift leads to a precarious situation. Huck is given an ultimatum as she readjusts to her old life.

episodes.name: Family Is a Four Letter Word
episodes.overview: Tensions rise as the group questions past events and plans for the future. Things get explosive as someone's abilities and loyalties are put to the test. A surprising discovery is made.

episodes.name: Quatervois
episodes.overview: Members of the group put a dangerous plan into motion, while others have serious reservations as more startling revelations come to light.

episodes.name: Who Are You?
episodes.overview: A member of the group becomes the target of an investigation. While some grow further apart, others begin to grow closer.

episodes.name: Blood and Lies
episodes.overview: As the group searches for answers, some struggle to find common ground while others question who can be trusted. A shocking message sets a new mission into motion.

episodes.name: Returning Point
episodes.overview: The group sets a new plan into motion as a relationship is leveraged and a betrayal forces others to take action.

episodes.name: Death and the Dead
episodes.overview: As the plan continues to unfold, tensions between the group and the CRM come to a dramatic head. While some rush to save an ally, difficult truths are brought to light.

episodes.name: The Last Light
episodes.overview: The remaining members of the group fight back enemies, both living and dead, on their quest to save the future.
